                                <h5>October 05, 2016</h5>
                                <h3>#MMGYTravels: DMAI 2016 in Minneapolis</h3>
                                <p>Our Director of Integrated Planning, Jessica Schultz, had the privilege of attending and speaking at DMAI, one of the largest events of the year for destination marketers. This year DMAI was hosted in Minneapolis – one of the best cities to visit in the summer.</p>
