                            <div class="content">
                                <h5>October 03, 2016</h5>
                                <h3>MMGY Global Adds Major Clients to Growing Global Portfolio</h3>
                                <p>MMGY Global announces substantial client growth in the third quarter across several travel industry categories. Club Med, Marriott’s Autograph Collection, National Geographic Partners, Tourism Ireland and the European Travel Commission have all contracted with the nation’s largest integrated travel marketing firm.</p>
