                                <h5>September 29, 2016</h5>
                                <h3>#MMGYTravels: Hotel Data Conference in Nashville</h3>
                                <p>Director of Data, Measurement &amp; Analytics, Chase Porter, recently attended and presented at the Hotel Data Conference in Nashville, TN. He and his wife found that “Music City” was filled with more than just music, including good food and plenty of larger-than-life sites to see.</p>
